          "mount": "turret",
          "linked": 0
        },
        {
          "weaponId": "laser_heavy",
          "mount": "turret",
          "linked": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Greater Bio-Ship",
      "desc": "Hive fleet capital organism the size of a small moon. She is the queen of her swarm, directing lesser bio-ships through psychic communion while her own weapon-organisms devastate everything in range. Destroying her disperses the fleet \u2014 but destroying her requires the kind of concentrated firepower that most navies cannot bring to bear before she closes to tentacle range.",
      "notes": "Hive fleet command organism. Destroying her breaks fleet cohesion. Size of a station.",
      "size": 26,
